      • selectByContexts

        public Dataset selectByContexts(ContextList contexts)
        Description copied from interface: Dataset
        Creating the sub Dataset (filtered Dataset) of this Dataset by selecting ratings whose contexts are in the specified context list. Context represents time, location, companion associated with a user when she/he is buying, studying, etc. Please see Context and ContextList for more details of context and context list.
        Parameters:
        contexts - Specified context list
        Returns:
        Sub Dataset whose contexts are in the specified context list

      • getCTSchema

        public ContextTemplateSchema getCTSchema()
        Description copied from interface: Dataset
        Getting schema of context template ContextTemplate. ContextTemplate is template for a context represented by the class Context. Context includes time, location, companion, etc. associated with a user when she/he is buying, studying, etc. For example, Time is the template for time context 31/10/2015 6:45. In other words, context is an instance of context template with specific value. A set of context templates is structured as the model which is called context template schema represented by interface ContextTemplateSchema. Please see Context, ContextTemplate and ContextTemplateSchema for more details of context, context template and context template schema.
        Returns:
        ContextTemplateSchema

      • getProvider

        public Provider getProvider()
        Description copied from interface: Dataset
        Some datasets like Scanner uses Provider to retrieve information from database because such datasets do not store information in memory. However other datasets such as Snapshot do not implement this method. This method return the internal provider of scanner.
        Returns:
        internal provider of scanner.
